data.description: Stunning End Unit Townhouse in Williamsburg, VA! Discover luxury living on a meticulously crafted end-unit townhouse offering a perfect blend of comfort and elegance. This property boasts: *End Unit with 6 ft Extension * Three Parking Spaces * Ample back & Side Yard Space, which can be fenced in * Partial Wooded Backyard View * Smart Home Features: Nest Wi-Fi thermostat, myQ Wi-Fi garage opener, Ring doorbell * Modern Kitchen: Quartz Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances * Upgraded Window Blinds for Style and Privacy * Convenient Outlets added in Utility Closet, Pantry, and Primary Bedroom Closet * Luxurious Bathrooms: 2 shower head Walk-In Shower with tile * Maytag Water Softener and Filtration System * Wired for Cable in Garage, Gigabit Speed Internet with Fiber * Fresh Air System for a Healthy Environment * Additional Recess Lighting Throughout * This home is beautiful and equipped with the latest technology and amenities.
